data.description: Welcome to Northridge Subdivision located less than 15 minutes from Hartsfield Jackson Airport and roughly 25 minutes from Downtown Atlanta. This well maintained 4-sided brick home has 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a private office, formal living, dining, and sunroom with a dual fireplace. You will enjoy the luxury of the oversized kitchen with plenty of natural sunlight. This house has a newer roof, new windows, new floor, and upgrades. Finish the basement and make it your dream! $5,000 grant available if buyer uses preferred lender, Chase.
